channel.title: Relenquish Source Release v2
channel.description:
[center][b]Relenquish Source Release v.2[/b][/center]
[center]Deleted - Will Reupload soon. Fixing a few things.[/center] [center][b]Features:[/b] Deadlock Fix Char File not found Fix Quests, Quest Saving, New Combat System New PVM New Items, correctly working Korasi with special Fightpits redone PVP is very good, nothing is overpowered.
ALOT of things fixed from the last version.
[b]Training Locations[/b] Taverly Dungeon Brimhaven Dungeon Rock Crabs Smoke Caves +Slayer tower Godwars Bandit Camp Kalphite Liar w/ KQ
[b]Activities[/b] Pest Control God Wars Basic Assualt Clue scrolls Barrows w/ Point system and chest rewards Fight Pits Fight Caves 63 waves JAD PVP-points and stores
Working Cannon (Still a little buggy, could be fixed up though) Vesta(full) Statius(full) D claws D KiteSheild Bandos Skimmy Bandos Kite Godswords w/ stance Godsword hilts and blades Spirit Sheild w/ sigils used on them to make the Spirit shields Elysian, arcane, ect D plate Proselyte Slayer helm Full Slayer helm Staff of Light draconic vissage Used with Anit to make dfs Teleportation Tabs Full bandos-chest, tassets, and boots Full armadyl-Chest, Skirt, and helm Some Colored Whips Saradomin Sword Zamorakian Spear Dragon Full Helm Astral Rune Not Invis Falador Sheild 3 Ardy Cloak
[b]Other:[/b] Acheivement Diary All skills quests- 2 for now more will be added Farming Cathreby north path no Tree patch by beach Easy access Farming Store ancient and lunar magiks Full Slayer Tower with Slayer Point System All Skill master That Give out Skillcapes(dont have Def) in General Store Lots of Drops and minimum Shoping Items(has basic PKing Equipment) Stores(melee, runes, armour, skillers wear, Fishing, pvp Points exchange and more Slayer point exchange Duradel Slayer master Vannaka Tasks Edit slayer task system that intergrates real slayer monsters Smoke Dungeon( Dustsdevils, Fire Giants, and Pyre Fiends) Will have Holiday Events
[img]http://www.upload.ee/image/1148244/cannon.bmp[/img]
[img]http://www.upload.ee/image/1148260/smokewell.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/1148251/inv.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/1148254/inv2.bmp[/img] [img]http://www.upload.ee/image/1148259/slayer_points.bmp[/img] [/center]
[center]Yeah, some of its pretty basic & is mostly like other PI's except for the cannon added (sort of glitchy) I tried converting it from shard. But it can be done better easily. Also it has a better quest saving system.
[b]Download links are at the top, it's packaged.[/b][/center]
